Actually, I'm fairly certain that it's Farmer Florent's little goat Genevieve! She must have escaped from her pen and gone on a little adventure. But she certainly caused a lot of trouble.
Well, it looks like we solved the mystery! Thank you so much for your help! Madame Florent! We've found Genevieve! Here you go.
